<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title><%= pageTitle %></title>
  <meta name="description" content="Free U.S. tax calculators for income tax, state income tax, sales tax, self-employment tax, and capital gains tax.">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="google-site-verification" content="TT2j7SgIafccBK-Nfk4ilXVIDXEJdSmyQJf2wL9QY0o" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.bunny.net">
  <link href="https://fonts.bunny.net/css?family=syne:700,800|dm-sans:400,500,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-5193834725888549" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- ── HEADER ── -->
  <header class="site-header">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="/" class="logo">
        <span class="logo-mark">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
            <rect x="1" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e"/>
            <rect x="11" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="1" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
            <rect x="11" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.25"/>
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span>MyTaxCalcs</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/calculators">Calculators</a>
        <a href="/california-income-tax-calculator">States</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <a class="nav-cta" href="/income-tax-calculator">Get Started</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- ── HERO ── -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg-grid"></div>
    <div class="hero-glow hero-glow-1"></div>
    <div class="hero-glow hero-glow-2"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">
        <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
        Free U.S. Tax Calculators
      </div>
      <h1>Simple tax estimates<br><em>start here</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Free calculators for federal income tax, state tax, sales tax,
        self-employment tax, and capital gains planning.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/income-tax-calculator">
          Calculate Income Tax
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#state-calculators">View State Calculators</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat"><strong>6</strong><span>Calculators</span></div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat"><strong>50</strong><span>States covered</span></div>
        <div class="stat-divider"></div>
        <div class="stat"><strong>Free</strong><span>Always</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── CALCULATOR CARDS ── -->
  <main>
    <div class="cards-wrapper">
      <div class="section-label">Tax Calculators</div>
      <div class="cards-grid">

        <a class="calc-card" href="/income-tax-calculator">
          <div class="calc-card-icon" style="background:#ecfdf5; color:#16a34a;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/><path d="M7 8h4M7 12h8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-card-body">
            <h2>Income Tax</h2>
            <p>Estimate federal taxable income, refund, amount owed, and effective tax rate.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

        <a class="calc-card" href="/self-employment-tax-calculator">
          <div class="calc-card-icon" style="background:#eff6ff; color:#2563eb;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-card-body">
            <h2>Self-Employment Tax</h2>
            <p>Estimate Social Security and Medicare tax for freelance, contractor, and gig income.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

        <a class="calc-card" href="/capital-gains-tax-calculator">
          <div class="calc-card-icon" style="background:#fef3c7; color:#d97706;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"/><polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-card-body">
            <h2>Capital Gains Tax</h2>
            <p>Estimate short-term and long-term tax on stocks, crypto, real estate, or other asset sales.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

        <a class="calc-card" href="/sales-tax-calculator">
          <div class="calc-card-icon" style="background:#fdf4ff; color:#9333ea;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="9" cy="21" r="1"/><circle cx="20" cy="21" r="1"/><path d="M1 1h4l2.68 13.39a2 2 0 001.98 1.61h9.72a2 2 0 001.98-1.61L23 6H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-card-body">
            <h2>Sales Tax</h2>
            <p>Estimate sales tax, combined tax rate, discount amount, and final purchase total.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

        <a class="calc-card" href="/payroll-tax-calculator">
          <div class="calc-card-icon" style="background:#fff1f2; color:#e11d48;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v16"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-card-body">
            <h2>Payroll Tax</h2>
            <p>Estimate paycheck withholding, Social Security, Medicare, state withholding, and net pay.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

        <a class="calc-card" href="/tax-refund-calculator">
          <div class="calc-card-icon" style="background:#f0fdf4; color:#15803d;">
            <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="23"/><path d="M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="calc-card-body">
            <h2>Tax Refund</h2>
            <p>Estimate your federal refund or amount owed using income, deductions, credits, and withholding.</p>
          </div>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── POPULAR STATE CALCULATORS ── -->
    <div class="popular-states-wrapper">
      <div class="section-label">Popular States</div>
      <div class="popular-states-grid">

        <a class="state-featured-card" href="/california-income-tax-calculator">
          <span class="state-badge">Popular</span>
          <div class="state-flag">🌉</div>
          <h3>California Tax</h3>
          <p>Estimate federal tax for California residents and prepare for state tax planning.</p>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

        <a class="state-featured-card" href="/texas-income-tax-calculator">
          <div class="state-flag">⭐</div>
          <h3>Texas Tax</h3>
          <p>Estimate federal tax for Texas residents with no broad-based state income tax.</p>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

        <a class="state-featured-card" href="/florida-income-tax-calculator">
          <div class="state-flag">☀️</div>
          <h3>Florida Tax</h3>
          <p>Estimate federal tax for Florida residents with no broad-based state income tax.</p>
          <span class="calc-card-link">Start Calculating <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></span>
        </a>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── ALL 50 STATES ── -->
    <section class="states-section" id="state-calculators">
      <div class="states-section-inner">
        <div class="section-header">
          <div class="section-label">All 50 States</div>
          <h2>State Income Tax Calculators</h2>
          <p>Choose your state to estimate federal tax and view state-specific tax calculator pages.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="state-list">
          <% states.forEach(function(state) { %>
            <a href="/<%= state.slug %>-income-tax-calculator"><%= state.name %></a>
          <% }) %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ── DISCLAIMER ── -->
    <div class="disclaimer-wrapper">
      <div class="disclaimer-inner">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
        <p><strong>Disclaimer:</strong> MyTaxCalcs provides estimates for educational purposes only. It is not tax, legal, accounting, or financial advice. Consult a qualified tax professional before making tax decisions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>

  <!-- ── FOOTER ── -->
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-inner">
      <div class="footer-grid">
        <div class="footer-brand">
          <a href="/" class="footer-logo">
            <span class="logo-mark">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                <rect x="1" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e"/>
                <rect x="11" y="1" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
                <rect x="1" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.5"/>
                <rect x="11" y="11" width="8" height="8" rx="2" fill="#22c55e" opacity="0.25"/>
              </svg>
            </span>
            MyTaxCalcs
          </a>
          <p>Free tax calculators for income tax, refunds, self-employment tax, capital gains tax, sales tax, payroll tax, and state income tax estimates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-column">
          <h3>Tax Calculators</h3>
          <a href="/calculators">All Calculators</a>
          <a href="/income-tax-calculator">Income Tax Calculator</a>
          <a href="/tax-refund-calculator">Tax Refund Calculator</a>
          <a href="/self-employment-tax-calculator">Self-Employment Tax</a>
          <a href="/capital-gains-tax-calculator">Capital Gains Tax</a>
          <a href="/sales-tax-calculator">Sales Tax Calculator</a>
          <a href="/payroll-tax-calculator">Payroll Tax Calculator</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-column">
          <h3>Site Links</h3>
          <a href="/california-income-tax-calculator">State Tax Calculators</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
          <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
          <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
          <a href="/disclaimer">Disclaimer</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-bottom">
        <p>© 2026 MyTaxCalcs.com. Estimates only. Not tax, legal, accounting, or financial advice.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
